# sump_pump_monitor

Dependencies:
Python: 
  pip install paho-mqtt       // mqtt libraries
  sudo pip install paho-mqtt  // systemd service runs as root, need to ensure root has access to python libraries

  pip install AWSIoTPythonSDK
  pip install rpi.gpio
  pip install numpy

Service definition needs to be in 
  ln ~/sump_pump_monitor/src/sump_pump_monitor.service /lib/systemd/system/sump_pump_monitor.service

  systemctl daemon-reload
  systemctl start|stop|restart sump_pump_monitor
  systemctl status sump_pump_monitor


